Though my eyes are dim [F]I can see heaven [C]clearly
[F]Though my voice grows [C]feeble I will [D7]sing just the [G7]same
In my [F]heart there’s a [C]song as I [G7]see the gates [C]open
[F]I'll sing [C]forever in [G7]His joyous re[C]frain
